  "full_text": "An update for openscap is now available for Red Hat Enterprise Linux 10.\n\nThe OpenSCAP suite enables integration of the Security Content AutomationProtocol (SCAP) line of standards. The openscap packages provide theOpenSCAP library and the oscap utility that provides various SCAPcapabilities.For detailed information on changes in this release, see the OpenSCAPrelease notes linked from the References section."
